    <p class="leading-7">
        A
        <span class="font-serif italic font-normal text-[18px]">{ageInWords}</span>
        year-old, fourth-year college student studying computer science at
        <span class="font-serif italic font-normal text-[18px]">Colorado State University</span>.
        Building elegant software for a variety of applications.
    </p>
</div>
